Summary: Saw in Northern sky,at least 6 silvery,fast moving
divs: sighting detailsi was just sitting outside the chili discgolf club........400 scottsville-chili road when i casually looked at theparking lot and noticed,initially 3 objects darting up in the sky a ways awaydarting back26 forth, blinking out,moving rapidly.then they were joined,at various timeswith 3 more- - -all the while darting back26 forth-- up26 down across the sky.......the moved slowly from a due north position to amore easterly position over a period of 9-10 minutes........both of ourattentions were distracted momentarily by a bike-rider that said hello and wenever saw the objects again tho we looked for approx. 5\6 min. after to see ifthey would come back!
